"Snow Roller brewed by Magic Hat Brewing Company, with an ABV 6.20%  This brew pours out a light brown color with a small white head. Snow Roller is a filtered brew you can see right though it. The smell rich with sweetness and grains. Now for the taste , it is bitter at first with a clean finish. Snow Roller has a nice balance to it, there is nothing overpowering in this brew.  Even the bitterness is nice in this brew. The mouthfeel is bold at first but snow roller has a clean finish. Overall I'm giving this brew a 4 out of 5.  Magic Hat Brewing Company, did a nice job with this brew.  I would buy this brew again."
